<p>Via <a href="https://twitter.com/climagic">climagic</a>'s <a href="https://twitter.com/climagic/status/694242271286431744?refsrc=email&amp;s=11">Suspend and reattach a process to screen</a>:</p>
<pre><code class="language-{.bash">longcmd ; [Ctrl-Z] ; bg ; disown ; screen ; reptyr $( pidof longcmd )
</code></pre>
